shorter/absent .**
- ** Missing Evidence for {Disease B Name }:** {Rule B} -> **MUST be vague or
unconfirmed .**
- ** Constraint :** DO NOT include any pathognomonic features (determining symptoms)
that would confirm A or B. Keep the severity and duration strictly in the "gray
zone".
